{"type":"message","id":"1b4bb5bb","parentId":"1d437f14","timestamp":"2026-03-19T18:20:00.267Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d Context Monitor] powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\miliger-context-manager\\scripts\\context-monitor.ps1\nCurrent time: Friday, March 20th, 2026 — 02:20 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-19 18:20 UTC"}],"timestamp":1773944400265}}
{"type":"message","id":"246ed5eb","parentId":"1b4bb5bb","timestamp":"2026-03-19T18:20:03.744Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The context monitor cron job ran. Let me check the context manager skill to see what needs to be done.","thinkingSignature":"188c0b24c94280e0ecc4ca0238816892cefdd6877911a771302de34d3b52eacd"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rcx3fa4597x9_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\miliger-context-manager\\scripts\\context-monitor.ps1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":161,"output":72,"cacheRead":37099,"cacheWrite":102,"totalTokens":37434,"cost":{"input":0.00006440000000000001,"output":0.000108,"cacheRead":0.00148396,"cacheWrite":0.0000153,"total":0.0016716600000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773944400266}}
{"type":"message","id":"76774940","parentId":"246ed5eb","timestamp":"2026-03-19T18:20:03.751Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rcx3fa4597x9_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Context Monitor for Windows\n# Monitors OpenClaw session context usage and alerts when threshold is reached\n\nparam(\n    [int]$Threshold = 60,\n    [string]$LogDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\\logs\",\n    [string]$LogFile = \"$LogDir\\context-monitor.log\"\n)\n\n# Ensure log directory exists\nif (!(Test-Path $LogDir)) {\n    New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $LogDir -Force | Out-Null\n}\n\nfunction Write-Log($Message) {\n    $timestamp = Get-Date -Format \"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\"\n    \"$timestamp - $Message\" | Out-File -Append -FilePath $LogFile\n    Write-Host \"$timestamp - $Message\"\n}\n\n# Get session list to check context usage\ntry {\n    # Use .NET Process to properly separate stdout and stderr\n    $psi = New-Object System.Diagnostics.ProcessStartInfo\n    $psi.FileName = \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\openclaw.cmd\"\n    $psi.Arguments = \"sessions --json\"\n    $psi.RedirectStandardOutput = $true\n    $psi.RedirectStandardError = $true\n    $psi.UseShellExecute = $false\n    $psi.CreateNoWindow = $true\n    \n    $process = New-Object System.Diagnostics.Process\n    $process.StartInfo = $psi\n    $process.Start() | Out-Null\n    \n    $stdout = $process.StandardOutput.ReadToEnd()\n    $stderr = $process.StandardError.ReadToEnd()\n    $process.WaitForExit()\n    \n    if ($stdout) {\n        # Extract JSON from stdout (find content between first { and last })\n        $jsonStart = $stdout.IndexOf('{')\n        $jsonEnd = $stdout.LastIndexOf('}')\n        \n        if ($jsonStart -ge 0 -and $jsonEnd -gt $jsonStart) {\n            $jsonContent = $stdout.Substring($jsonStart, $jsonEnd - $jsonStart + 1)\n            $data = $jsonContent | ConvertFrom-Json -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n            \n            if ($data -and $data.sessions) {\n                # Find main session\n                $mainSession = $data.sessions | Where-Object { $_.key -eq 'agent:main:main' } | Select-Object -First 1\n                \n                if ($mainSession -and $mainSession.totalTokens -and $mainSession.contextTokens) {\n                    $used = $mainSession.totalTokens\n                    $total = $mainSession.contextTokens\n                    $usage = [math]::Round(($used / $total) * 100)\n                    \n                    Write-Log \"Context usage: ${usage}% (${used}/${total} tokens)\"\n                    \n                    if ($usage -ge $Threshold) {\n                        Write-Log \"WARNING: Context usage ${usage}% exceeds threshold ${Threshold}%\"\n                        \n                        # Check memory files\n                        $memoryDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\"\n                        $memoryLite = \"$memoryDir\\MEMORY-LITE.md\"\n                        \n                        if (Test-Path $memoryLite) {\n                            $content = Get-Content $memoryLite -Raw -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n                            $wordCount = ($content -split '\\s+').Count\n                            Write-Log \"MEMORY-LITE.md: $wordCount words\"\n                        }\n                        \n                        Write-Log \"ALERT: Consider starting a new session to reset context\"\n                    } else {\n                        Write-Log \"Context usage normal: ${usage}%\"\n                    }\n                } else {\n                    Write-Log \"Main session found but no token info available\"\n                }\n            } else {\n                Write-Log \"No sessions data found in JSON\"\n            }\n        } else {\n            Write-Log \"Could not find JSON content in output\"\n        }\n    } else {\n        Write-Log \"No output from sessions command\"\n    }\n} catch {\n    Write-Log \"Error checking context: $_\"\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773944403749}}
{"type":"message","id":"35172413","parentId":"76774940","timestamp":"2026-03-19T18:20:06.501Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The context monitor script ran. Let me check the log file to see what it recorded.","thinkingSignature":"fa99a03e9fce90c3b2ab5c2e4a2832b71caeb2f47156d723d39694755178343f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_f3nfktpdmf1z_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Command \"if (Test-Path $env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\\logs\\context-monitor.log) { Get-Content $env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\\logs\\context-monitor.log -Tail 10 } else { Write-Host 'Log file not found' }\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1184,"output":113,"cacheRead":37099,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38396,"cost":{"input":0.0004736,"output":0.0001695,"cacheRead":0.00148396,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00212706}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773944403752}}
{"type":"message","id":"e717060f","parentId":"35172413","timestamp":"2026-03-19T18:20:06.737Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_f3nfktpdmf1z_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"2026-03-20 02:03:29 - ALERT: Consider starting a new session to reset context\r\n2026-03-20 02:05:08 - Context usage: 77% (153920/200000 tokens)\r\n2026-03-20 02:05:08 - WARNING: Context usage 77% exceeds threshold 60%\r\n2026-03-20 02:05:08 - ALERT: Consider starting a new session to reset context\r\n2026-03-20 02:10:14 - Context usage: 77% (153920/200000 tokens)\r\n2026-03-20 02:10:14 - WARNING: Context usage 77% exceeds threshold 60%\r\n2026-03-20 02:10:14 - ALERT: Consider starting a new session to reset context\r\n2026-03-20 02:15:17 - Context usage: 77% (153920/200000 tokens)\r\n2026-03-20 02:15:17 - WARNING: Context usage 77% exceeds threshold 60%\r\n2026-03-20 02:15:17 - ALERT: Consider starting a new session to reset context"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":230,"aggregated":"2026-03-20 02:03:29 - ALERT: Consider starting a new session to reset context\r\n2026-03-20 02:05:08 - Context usage: 77% (153920/200000 tokens)\r\n2026-03-20 02:05:08 - WARNING: Context usage 77% exceeds threshold 60%\r\n2026-03-20 02:05:08 - ALERT: Consider starting a new session to reset context\r\n2026-03-20 02:10:14 - Context usage: 77% (153920/200000 tokens)\r\n2026-03-20 02:10:14 - WARNING: Context usage 77% exceeds threshold 60%\r\n2026-03-20 02:10:14 - ALERT: Consider starting a new session to reset context\r\n2026-03-20 02:15:17 - Context usage: 77% (153920/200000 tokens)\r\n2026-03-20 02:15:17 - WARNING: Context usage 77% exceeds threshold 60%\r\n2026-03-20 02:15:17 - ALERT: Consider starting a new session to reset context","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773944406735}}
{"type":"message","id":"d4cf5888","parentId":"e717060f","timestamp":"2026-03-19T18:20:12.344Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The context usage is at 77% (153920/200000 tokens). The threshold is 60%, so it's been alerting. This is expected behavior from the context monitor. The system already has a context manager skill that should handle this. But let me check if there's a MEMORY-LITE.md that needs updating, and also check the session status.\n\nGiven the time is 02:20 AM, it's late night - I should stay quiet unless there's something urgent. The context usage at 77% is high but not critical. The human should be sleeping.\n\nSince this is a heartbeat/cron context monitor, I should just log this and stay quiet. The system is functioning as expected.","thinkingSignature":"7048210f67bbc513493c8a1c277b85a0185315e71efe70cab14e6ee9da18735b"},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1571,"output":149,"cacheRead":37099,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38819,"cost":{"input":0.0006284000000000001,"output":0.0002235,"cacheRead":0.00148396,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0023358600000000004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773944406737}}
